TY  - JOUR
AU  - Christopherson, Jon A.
AU  - Ferson, Wayne E.
AU  - Glassman, Debra A.
T1  - Conditioning Manager Alphas on Economic Information: Another Look at the Persistence of Performance
PY  - 1998
Y1  - 1998/01/01
DO  - 10.1093/rfs/11.1.0111
JO  - The Review of Financial Studies
JA  - Rev Financ Stud
VL  - 11
IS  - 1
SP  - 111
EP  - 142
SN  - 0893-9454
AB  - This article presents evidence on persistence in the relative investment performance of large, institutional equity managers. Similar to existing evidence for mutual funds, we find persistent performance concentrated in the managers with poor prior-period performance measures. A conditional approach, using time-varying measures of risk and abnormal performance, is better able to detect this persistence and to predict the future performance of the funds than are traditional methods.
Y2  - 3/26/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1093/rfs/11.1.0111
ER  - 



